data.description: Looking for a new home without the "cookie cutter" vibe? Welcome home to this newly renovated beautiful piece of history located in the up and coming downtown area in the city of Woodruff. This home has been completely updated inside and out with new roof, HVAC system, plumbing, electrical, and more! As you approach the house, you will immediately notice the beautiful columns and wrap around porch perfect for a porch swing and rocking chairs. As you walk in the house, you will see the high 10 ft ceilings and open floor plan that makes this home feel enormous. The kitchen has been updated with granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances, and white shaker cabinets with soft close doors and drawers. As you walk down the hallway you will notice 2 bedrooms on either side big walk in closets in addition to a full bathroom. The huge master bedroom boasts two large walk in closets and a double barn door leading to the bathroom with a tiled walk-in shower and new vanity.   This is an unbeatable deal with the items that will convey. Washer, Dryer, Refrigerator, 2 large powered sheds and more.   You can't beat the location as it is just a few blocks from all of the new fun things to do on Main St. in Woodruff as well as only 15 min from Five Forks and close to I-85 and BMW.   This home is only 5 mins away from the new BMW battery plant that just broke ground. Snag this home while you can in the up and coming Woodruff area.  **HOME comes with a 1-YEAR Warranty**    Trash and sewer  through the City of Woodruff $100 Bi-monthly
